query: SELECT bg.id, bg.eventoId, bg.numero, bg.dataGrupo, bg.horarioFormandos, bg.limiteFormandos, bg.ativo, e.tipoEvento FROM briefing_grupo bg JOIN eventos e ON bg.eventoId = e.id WHERE e.turmaId = (SELECT id FROM turmas WHERE codigo = '654' LIMIT 1) ORDER BY bg.eventoId, bg.numero
